                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Similar to uranium measurements were performed for CH2",
                "scatterers at angles near 2. degr. Then multiple-",
                "scattering corrections were made by use of the known",
                "hydrogen and carbon differential cross sections",
                "extrapolated to the small-angle region. These",
                "corrections took account of the energy dependence of",
                "the multiply scattered neutrons. The corrected CH2",
                "results normalized to the corresponding theoretically",
                "expected cross sections (D.J.Hughers+,R,BNL-325,1955)",
                "were utilized to obtain final absolute differential",
                "cross sections for uranium."
              ]
            }
          ],
